|    1005  | rsWord  |    1 |     RW | 0..4       |             2 | Control Mode (cmPi = 0,  cmPid = 1, cmLin = 2,  cmFill = 3,  cOff = 4)
|    1006  | rsFloat |    2 |     RW | 0..X,00    |          0,15 | Pressure Min 
