|    1036  | rsWord  |    1 |     RW | 0..5       |             0 | Relay 2 Mode (Off = 0, Alarm = 1, Low = 2, High = 3, SecondPump = 4, FirstPump = 5)
|    1037  | rsWord  |    1 |     RW | 0..999     |             5 | Relay 2 Low Delay Time (Seconds) 
|    1038  | rsWord  |    1 |     RW | 0..999     |             5 | Relay 2 High Delay Time (Seconds)
|    1039  | rsWord  |    1 |     RW | 0..100     |            90 | Relay 2 Second Pump Start Percent
|    1040  | rsWord  |    1 |     RW | 0..100     |            50 | Relay 2 Second Pump Stop Percent
